00:06:17.840 --> 00:06:21.080
I hate and I love.

00:06:21.080 --> 00:06:24.020
Why do I do this, perhaps you ask?

00:06:24.020 --> 00:06:25.770
I do not know.

00:06:25.770 --> 00:06:30.280
